Castellan					KEY:Cavalier Archetype ~ Castellan				CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.CavalierArchetype.CavalierMount.CavalierCavaliersCharge.CavalierExpertTrainer.CavalierMightyCharge.CavalierDemandingChallenge.CavalierSupremeCharge	PRECLASS:1,Cavalier=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Cavalier Archetype ~ Castellan],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,TYPE.CavalierHeavyArmorProficiency,TYPE.CavalierMount,TYPE.CavalierCavaliersCharge,TYPE.CavalierExpertTrainer,TYPE.CavalierDemandingChallenge,TYPE.CavalierSupremeCharge]																											DESC:A castellan is a cavalier who dedicates himself to the defense of a castle or walled city. Though not as celebrated as the cavaliers who ride forth to take on distant foes, the castellan is no less brave or important, for the castellan and his allies are the last line of defense for those who depend on the fortification for protection.																																																																ABILITY:Cavalier Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Castellan ~ Castle Defender|PRECLASS:1,Cavalier=1	ABILITY:Cavalier Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Castellan ~ Castle Lore|PRECLASS:1,Cavalier=3	ABILITY:Cavalier Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Castellan ~ Guard Companion|PRECLASS:1,Cavalier=4	ABILITY:Cavalier Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Castellan ~ Mighty Defense|PRECLASS:1,Cavalier=11	ABILITY:Cavalier Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Castellan ~ Defending Challenge|PRECLASS:1,Cavalier=12	ABILITY:Cavalier Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Castellan ~ Supreme Defense|PRECLASS:1,Cavalier=20																																																																		COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.9	ASPECT:Archetype Base Class|Cavalier

Castle Defender				KEY:Castellan ~ Castle Defender				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Cavalier Class Feature.ArchetypeAbility.SpecialQuality.CavalierMount																																																																																													DESC:A castellan gains a +%1 bonus to AC and an additional +%1 bonus on attack rolls when he is on higher ground. He also gains an additional +%1 bonus to AC and Reflex saves when he has cover other than soft cover from other creatures.|1+(CavalierLVL>=11)	DESC: He gains evasion (as a rogue) when he has cover (but not soft cover) against the source of the attack. This works even when wearing medium or heavy armor.|PREVARGTEQ:CavalierLVL,6|PREVARLT:CavalierLVL,16	DESC: He gains improved evasion (as a rogue) when he has cover (but not soft cover) against the source of the attack. This works even when wearing medium or heavy armor.|PREVARGTEQ:CavalierLVL,16																																																																																																																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.9
Castle Lore					KEY:Castellan ~ Castle Lore					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Cavalier Class Feature.ArchetypeAbility.SpecialQuality.CavalierCavaliersCharge																																																																																												DESC:The castellan gains a +%1 bonus on initiative checks and Knowledge (engineering), Knowledge (local), Knowledge (nobility), Perception, and Stealth checks when he is in urban terrain, including fortifications. A castellan in an urban environment can always act in a surprise round, though he remains flat-footed until he acts.|floor((CavalierLVL+2)/5)*2																																																																																																																																																																																																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.9
Guard Companion				KEY:Castellan ~ Guard Companion				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Cavalier Class Feature.ArchetypeAbility.SpecialQuality.CavalierExpertTrainer																																																																		DEFINE:AnimalCompanionLVL|0	DEFINE:AnimalCompanionMasterLVL|0	DEFINE:AnimalCompanionGranted|0	DEFINE:CompanionMasterLVL_Druid|0				DESC:The castellan forms a bond with an animal companion that serves as a guard. While most castellans select birds or canines, the castellan can choose any animal companions available to rangers. This ability functions like the druid nature bond ability, except that the castellan's effective druid level is equal to his cavalier level â€“ 3 and his animal companion doesn't gain the share spells special ability.																																																				ABILITY:Internal|AUTOMATIC|Animal Companion ~ Standard Companions	ABILITY:Internal|AUTOMATIC|Animal Companion ~ Base																																																																																																																				BONUS:VAR|AnimalCompanionGranted|1	BONUS:VAR|AnimalCompanionMasterLVL|CompanionMasterLVL_Druid	BONUS:VAR|CompanionMasterLVL_Druid|CavalierLVL-3			SOURCEPAGE:p.9
Mighty Defense				KEY:Castellan ~ Mighty Defense				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Cavalier Class Feature.ArchetypeAbility.SpecialQuality.CavalierMightyCharge																																																																																												DESC:When the castellan readies an action to make a melee attack against a creature that is not yet adjacent to him, he doubles the threat range of any melee weapons wielded during the attack. This increase doesn't stack with other effects that increase the threat range of his weapons. In addition, the cavalier can attempt a free dirty trick, disarm, sunder, or trip combat maneuver if his readied attack is successful. This free combat maneuver doesn't provoke an attack of opportunity.																																																																																																																																																																																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.9
Defending Challenge			KEY:Castellan ~ Defending Challenge				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Cavalier Class Feature.ArchetypeAbility.SpecialQuality.CavalierDemandingChallenge																																																																																											DESC:The castellan takes no penalty to Armor Class when using his challenge ability.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.9
Supreme Defense				KEY:Castellan ~ Supreme Defense				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Cavalier Class Feature.ArchetypeAbility.SpecialQuality.CavalierSupremeCharge																																																																																												DESC:Whenever the castellan readies an action to make a melee attack against a creature that is not yet adjacent to him, his readied attack deals double the normal amount of damage (or triple the damage if using a brace weapon against a charge). In addition, if the cavalier confirms a critical hit on the readied attack, the target is stunned for 1d4 rounds. A successful Will save (DC %1) reduces this to being staggered for 1d4 rounds.|10+floor(CavalierLVL/2)+STR																																																																																																																																																																																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.9

