Tactician					KEY:Drill Sergeant ~ Tactician				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Fighter Class Feature.ArchetypeAbility.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.FighterBravery																																																																																											DESC:A drill sergeant gains the cavalier's tactician class feature, treating his fighter level as his cavalier level for the purposes of this ability. He receives a teamwork feat as a bonus feat. He must meet the prerequisites for this feat. As a standard action, the drill sergeant can grant this feat to all allies within 30 feet who can see and hear him. Allies retain the use of this bonus feat for %1 rounds. Allies do not need to meet the prerequisites of these bonus feats. The drill sergeant can use this ability %2 times per day.|3+FighterLVL/2|1+FighterLVL/5																																																																																																																											BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Teamwork Feat|1																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.11	ASPECT:NAME|Tactician
Weapon Training				KEY:Drill Sergeant ~ Weapon Training			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Fighter Class Feature.ArchetypeAbility.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.WeaponTraining1																																																																																											DESC:A drill sergeant gains weapon training with one group of weapons. He doesn't gain weapon training with other groups at later levels, though his weapon training does improve with his chosen weapon group.																																																																																							ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Fighter ~ Weapon Training																																																																																							BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Weapon Training I|1																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.11
Greater Tactician				KEY:Drill Sergeant ~ Greater Tactician			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Fighter Class Feature.ArchetypeAbility.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.WeaponTraining2																																																																																											DESC:The drill sergeant gains the cavalier's greater tactician class feature. The drill sergeant receives an additional teamwork feat as a bonus feat. He must meet the prerequisites for this feat. The drill sergeant can grant this feat to his allies using the tactician ability. Using the tactician ability is a swift action.																																																																																																																																																																			BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Teamwork Feat|1																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.11
Weapon Trainer				KEY:Drill Sergeant ~ Weapon Trainer				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Fighter Class Feature.ArchetypeAbility.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.WeaponTraining3																																																																																											DESC:When a drill sergeant wields a weapon he has weapon training in, all allies within 30 feet who can see and hear the drill sergeant gain half his weapon training bonus when they wield any weapon from the same weapon group. This bonus doesn't stack with any weapon training bonus an ally already possesses.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.11
Master Tactician				KEY:Drill Sergeant ~ Master Tactician			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Fighter Class Feature.ArchetypeAbility.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.WeaponTraining4																																																																																											DESC:The drill sergeant gains the cavalier's master tactician class feature. The drill sergeant receives an additional teamwork feat as a bonus feat. He must meet the prerequisites for this feat. The drill sergeant can grant this feat to his allies using the tactician ability. Whenever the drill sergeant uses the tactician ability, he grants any two teamwork feats that he knows. He can select from any of his teamwork feats, not just his bonus feats.																																																																																																																																														BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Teamwork Feat|1																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.11

